jill and john freidenrich center for translational research the stanford challenge jill and john freidenrich center for translational research jill and john freidenrich center for translational research since 2006 the jill and john freidenrich center for translational research has supported work that applies basic research findings to practical health interventions at the stanford cancer institute in 2012 the center will move to its own new building the freidenrich center will house the stanford center for clinical and translational education and research spectrum and host clinical trials having all these resources under one roof will facilitate easy interaction between clinical trial patients and researchers learn more article groundbreaking event new freidenrich center to accelerate clinical trials web site freidenrich center for translational research comments are closed
